# Create/import a repository;
# Add a deployment key (an SSH key for my local linux box);
# Delete that repository;
# Add SSH key for account: oops! that key is used as a deployment key!

Quick fix, works if you imported that repo:

# Re-import the same repository;
# Add the same deployment key to it;
# Remove that deployment key;
# Remove that repo;
# Whoa, it works now!

